<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_213" id="106v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l1">Adeln von Schyppff </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l2">Amptman cʒu Bẏſſchofſheim</ab>
</del></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><del rend="crossout"><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l3"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Adel / vns hat <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan> C fügel vnſer <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vvie Jm nü </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l6">in <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincʒ 
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l5">lande auff 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſechs </del></ab></add>
<del rend="strikethrough"> gepiete / vier pferde</del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l8">
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1587385902401_14">der <expan>ſtraffe<ex>n</ex></expan> darauff Jr </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1587385907836_19">von <expan>ſeıne<ex>m</ex></expan> wegen </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1587385911549_24">cʒugepieten vnd </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1587385938861_30">geleẏten habt Sechs </ab><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1587385942381_35">pferde </ab></add> genomen 
<del rend="strikethrough">ſein worden </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_r1l7">vnd </ab></add> / der Jm cʒwey wider vvorden ſein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l11">die 
<del rend="strikethrough">e </del> andern viere Jm noch auſſen ſteen / <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_line_1576674565265_11024">Jm durch <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günſtige hilff vnd <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l16">beweiſen wöllet / 
<del rend="strikethrough">ob </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_213_line_1576674568002_11029">daʒ </ab></add> Jm die v̈brigen vier pferde auch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_213_r1l17">widervverden / Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
</del>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_213" id="106v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><del rend="crossout">Adeln von Schyppff, amptman czu Bysschofsheim
                        </del></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><del rend="crossout"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> Adel, uns hat
                                    <expan>fürg<ex>elegt</ex></expan>
<expan>C<ex>onrad</ex></expan> Fügel, unser
                                    <expan>b<ex>urger,</ex></expan> wie im nü in
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> gnedigen
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von Meincz <add>lande auff
                                </add><add>der <expan>straffe<ex>n</ex></expan>, darauff ir von
                                        <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan> wegen czu gepieten und
                                geleyten habt, sechs pferde</add> genomen <add>und</add> der im
                            czwey wider worden sein, die andern viere im noch aussen steen.
                                    <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir im durch
                                    <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen
                                <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> günstige hilff und
                                    <expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> beweisen wöllet, <add>daz</add>
                            im die übrigen vier pferde auch widerwerden, als etc. Das
                                    <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. </del></ab>
</div>
